Title: Worcester plume pitched flashing
Description: A genuine Worcester part, this pitched flashing kit is suitable for use with Greenstar CDI Classic 29, 34 and 38 and CDI Classic LPG 29, 34 and 38. This kit seals a roof to prevent the ingress of water.

Title: Deks Industries Seldek SDA101B number 1 flashing system 50-170mm (5 per box )
Description: Used to install a flash on tile or slate roofs quickly and economically, this Deks Industries Seldek flashing system is suitable for 50 - 170mm flues. Made of aluminium, this weathering slate won't stain or corrode roofs or guttering. The watertight cone is simply trimmed to fit on-site to fit and has been cleverly locked to a high-grade and malleable 99.9% pure aluminium base.

Title: Baxi Multifit flat roof flashing
Description: It may be tempting to opt for a low cost spare part, but do consider the impact that this may have. Counterfeit parts are typically substandard, manufactured from poor quality materials thus impacting on the design and strength of the product. In the event of a system failure or - in a worst case scenario, an accident - the ultimate responsibility lies with the service and repair engineer rather than the product which was ill-chosen for the application. It is always reccommended you go for an official part, such as this one.
